Muchidzidzo che[[Taranyika]] (Geography), mazuva e[[Tsazahusiku]] anoitika March 20-21 neSeptember 20-21. Pamazuva aya ''Denderedzwa reChiedza'' rinocheka North pole neSouth pole - mativi ose eAkiso anenge ari hhambwe dzakafanana kubva kuzuva - hapana divi rinenge riri ''pedyo'' nezuva kudarika rimwe. Zvakare hapana divi reAkiso rinenge rakanongedza kune zuva. Pam
